headline: Invitation Homes' Q3 FFO In Line, Revenues Beat, Rents Improve Y/Y
summary: Invitation Homes posts steady Q3 core FFO of 47 cents per share as higher rents offset lower occupancy, prompting a slight full-year outlook raise.
